&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;The &lt;strong&gt;Director, Revenue Cycle&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;is the enterprise owner of end-to-end revenue cycle performance across Upward Health’s operations. This role is accountable for the accuracy, efficiency, and scalability of all revenue cycle functions—including charge capture, coding, billing, claims submission, denial management, and collections.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
