&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;The role partners closely with finance, operations, clinical, and IT leadership to ensure that revenue cycle processes are aligned with organizational goals and evolving payer requirements. The Director will also lead teams across billing, coding, and accounts receivable functions, establishing a culture of accountability, continuous improvement, and data-driven decision-making.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
