&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Manage risk adjustment operations and oversee execution of the annual Risk Adjustment strategy to meet internal and external goals, including reporting, operational execution, and performance monitoring tied to RAF, Medicaid risk score, and acuity outcomes.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:257}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Manage and provide oversight of risk&amp;nbsp;adjustment&amp;nbsp;client data files, including review, prioritization, coordination, and operational use of data outputs to&amp;nbsp;identify&amp;nbsp;opportunities, support intervention planning, and inform risk adjustment decision-making.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:257}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
